es/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab28109be188f1d727236ca27d562e2bcf019626","tid":317153,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/2cd041af20c88cb896dbd273fe030e07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F2cd041af20c88cb896dbd273fe030e07.jpg&h=66582caa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d378309e183c7745a8b11e59e52b3a141de8d9ee","tid":317153,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"入錯黑社會係要d代價"},{"pid":"28e67eb95d25af02de252391b0e5394024011df5","tid":317153,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔通去幫一個走咗嘅人撐場乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你咩<br />\n鳩達佢地吹雞去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲唔係用完即棄？"},{"pid":"fae732e7a2100dd6ef8c3556dba68cf16792faae","tid":317153,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朱寶生同李政熙幾個月之前已經同熱狗割咗席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哇咁仆街同熱狗割席<br />\n熱狗冇爆佢地「黑材料」已經算好厚道啦<br />\n真係正直"},{"pid":"802739b0d18e562546522b6658e84491a6d4b9f2","tid":317153,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:13:17.000Z","msg":"熱共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李生page<br />\n本人今日在九龍城法院就一單襲警案的指控上庭，有一Facebook專頁就本案作了錯誤失實的陳述，為免對本案帶來任何壞影響，本人必須在此澄清。<br />\n<br />\n今日本人於庭上並無進行任何答辯，名為「熱血時報」的專頁向大眾發放本人今日已否認控罪的消息，並不屬實。<br />\n<br />\n我現要求該專頁向本人道歉，撒回錯誤的陳述，並向公眾澄清，以正視聽。"},{"pid":"e7c121e4f1a6108c59a6cea1bc87ad3fba8ebb3f","tid":317153,"uid":122929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毓民反而有去聽審，雙鄭一陳就唔見人!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢哋兩個人要上法庭受罪，都係因為熱狗吹雞護教主啫，教主作為當事人，唔去撐場講唔過去。"},{"pid":"d410258136cf82901f90c40d8fcc1e68485ab9ee","tid":317153,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>毓民反而有去聽審，雙鄭一陳就唔見人!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢哋兩個人要上法庭受罪，都係因為熱狗吹雞護教主啫，教主作為當事人，唔去撐場講唔過去。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教主做返應該要做既事，相比之下熱狗真係差好遠"}]}